sharp / @img/sharp-libvips-*  (LGPL-3.0-or-later)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Image processing uses `sharp` (Apache-2.0), which dynamically links prebuilt
libvips binaries published as `@img/sharp-libvips-<platform>` under
LGPL-3.0-or-later. These are separate, dynamically-linked native libraries (not
statically compiled into Nodaro), which is compatible with redistribution. The
libvips source corresponding to those binaries is available from the sharp /
libvips projects: https://github.com/lovell/sharp and https://www.libvips.org

